# Navigation

- Use NavigationStack and NavigationPath; use .navigationDestination(for:) for type-safe routing
- Use TabView as root with per-tab NavigationStack
- Use .sheet and .fullScreenCover for sheets
- On macOS use NavigationSplitView for sidebar on larger screens
- Handle deep links with onOpenURL
